release.body:
<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at 3.8.x -->

## What's Changed
### Breaking Changes 🛠
* BREAKING: update dependency org.yaml:snakeyaml to v2 by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8905

### Improvements ⭐
* fix: allow to disable  disable `ServiceReadyHealthIndicator` via configuration by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8836
* remove parallelism from default methods in AnnotationScanner by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8906
* Prevent multiple date headers with file responses by @jameskleeh in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8872
* imp: Add STANDARD_HEADERS list by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8903

### Docs 📖
* docs: fix Route Compile-Time validation by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8877

### Tests ✅
* test: HTTP Server TCK Health endpoint by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8862
* test: HTTP Server TCK LOG body and contains string by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8861

### Dependency Upgrades 🚀
* micronaut-crac 1.1.2
* micronaut-serialization to 1.5.2 (#8895)
* micronaut-kafka to 4.5.2 (#8878)
* micronaut-aot to 1.1.2 (#8874)
* micronaut-gcp to 4.8.1 (#8875)

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/compare/v3.8.6...v3.8.7
